{"tid":1534883,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"漁灣邨地盤工業意外　男子高處墮下不治","createTime":"2019-09-03T07:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T20:11:39.000Z","uid":227929,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0001a008c7e9778b2914a8b5b31bedeb7c51a916","tid":1534883,"uid":227929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:00:58.000Z","msg":"漁灣邨地盤工業意外　男子高處墮下不治<br />\n<br />\n柴灣發生工業意外，一名男子在漁灣邨一個地盤約兩米高的地方墮下，其後證實不治。事發在中午左右，救護員到場時男子已陷入昏迷，警方正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n2019-09-03 14:50:27<br />\n<br />\nSource:RTHK 即時新聞<br />\n<br />\n屯門跳樓<br />\n西貢謀殺<br />\n尖咀浮屍<br />\n柴灣墮樓<br />\n<br />\n仲有中午嗰陣唔係應該食飯時間㗎喇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdcfcdc28f460c6280af85d1c4e5d382e008dd55","tid":1534883,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:01:08.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d70cd85bb300f7b543e8f98e7e45fa188caddd25","tid":1534883,"uid":227929,"like":0,"dislike":0,